IMAPAccount marliere.net
Host mail.marliere.net
Port 143
User ricardo@marliere.net
PassCmd "pass marliere.net"

IMAPStore remote
Account marliere.net

MaildirStore local
SubFolders Verbatim
# The trailing "/" is important
Path ~/mail/marliere.net/all/
Inbox ~/mail/marliere.net/all/inbox

MaildirStore trash
SubFolders Verbatim
# The trailing "/" is important
Path ~/mail/marliere.net/trash/
Inbox ~/mail/marliere.net/trash/inbox

Channel all
Far :remote:
Near :local:
Patterns * !archive !spam !sent !INBOX !drafts !important
Create Both
Remove Both
#Sync Pull New ReNew Push Flags
Sync Pull New Upgrade
Expunge None

Channel sync
Far :remote:
Near :local:
Create Both
Remove Both
Patterns archive spam sent INBOX drafts important trash
Sync All
Expunge Both

Channel trash
Far :remote:
Near :trash:
Patterns * !archive !spam !sent !INBOX !drafts !important !trash
Create Both
Remove Both
Expunge Both
